  Tracer1         #Tracer1 is for the reaction of ebullition of CH4, which produces Tracer1
  Tracer2         #Tracer2 is for homogeneous plant-mediated CH4 removal, Tracer2 is made to have high concentration at the root layer
  Tracer3         # Tracer3 is for heterogeneous plant-mediated CH4 removal, Tracer3 is made to have high concentration within the root cells
  CH4(aq)
  SO4--
  H2S(aq)
  #### NOTE: End of auto-inserted primary species ####
/



DECOUPLED_EQUILIBRIUM_REACTIONS
  #### NOTE: Beginning of auto-inserted primary species ####
  DOM1
